The paper deals with auctions, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and algorithmic mechanism design (cs.EC). The concept of efficiency is also relevant to optimization (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper proposes a new notion of efficiency, which involves maximizing revenue, and provides approximation algorithms, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG).
